profile: Welcome to Integrity Contracting Corp. We are a quality Home Additions, framing and Custom Homes Construction company that delivers projects on time, on budget and in quality way at a fair and reasonable market price. Serving Toronto and the GTA. And now serving the Innisfil-Barrie area ABOUT US Find us on Facebook! The majority of our business comes from word of mouth and repeated business thanks to consistent customer satisfaction. We achieve this through practicing exquisite attention to detail and excellence in customer service. Our mission statement includes preserving our level of integrity, professionalism, honesty and fairness in our relationships with our customers. Our services include: *New Homes Framing *Water Proofing *Excavation *Post & Beam Timber Construction *Framing & Timber Frames *Demolition *Home Additions *Decks & Fences *Commercial Wood Roof Systems *Glue-Lam Structures *I.C.F foundation *Undepinning

profile:
Welcome to Open Concept 

The company specializes in structural engineering and renovations. OCEC LTD was founded to be able to help others live their lives without unwanted obstructions. It may be a wall, a duct hump or post in the basement that is in the way of your pool table or a home gym or simply in the middle of a room. Whatever the case may be itâ€™s not IM'possible. Our innovative approach to basement post removal has been designed and approved by qualified engineers with many satisfied customers. The method does not require any welding or major beam replacements. We have also made it possible through our ingenuity to be able to sink beams into the joists to have a perfectly flat ceiling finish on both the first and/or second floors of your home.

We are an insured business from both and engineering and construction stand point. 

Liability Insurance on Construction and Engineering Services. 

We're social here:

https://www.facebook.com/ocecltd
